<h3 id="zi-ding-yi-mo-ban"><a class="header-anchor" href="#zi-ding-yi-mo-ban" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> 自定义模板</h3>
<p>可以自定义备选项</p>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;template&gt;\n  &lt;el-select v-model=\&quot;value6\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;请选择\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;el-option v-for=\&quot;item in cities\&quot; :key=\&quot;item.value\&quot; :label=\&quot;item.label\&quot; :value=\&quot;item.value\&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;span style=\&quot;float: left\&quot;&gt;{{ item.label }}&lt;/span&gt;\n      &lt;span style=\&quot;float: right; color: #8492a6; font-size: 13px\&quot;&gt;{{ item.value }}&lt;/span&gt;\n    &lt;/el-option&gt;\n  &lt;/el-select&gt;\n&lt;/template&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\n  export default {\n    data() {\n      return {\n        cities: [{\n          value: 'Beijing',\n          label: '北京'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Shanghai',\n          label: '上海'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Nanjing',\n          label: '南京'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Chengdu',\n          label: '成都'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Shenzhen',\n          label: '深圳'\n        }, {\n          value: 'Guangzhou',\n          label: '广州'\n        }],\n        value6: ''\n      }\n    }\n  }\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><template>
  <el-select v-model="value6" placeholder="请选择">
    <el-option v-for="item in cities" :key="item.value" :label="item.label" :value="item.value">
      <span style="float: left">{{ item.label }}</span>
      <span style="float: right; color: #8492a6; font-size: 13px">{{ item.value }}</span>
    </el-option>
  </el-select>
</template>


</div>
                    <p>将自定义的 HTML 模板插入<code>el-option</code>的 slot 中即可。</p>

